libbc-io (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * File primitives: open/close wrappers, path and inode helpers.
  * Memory-mapped file helpers (mmap / munmap).
  * Buffered stream with readahead / sequential / random advise hints.
  * Full sanitizer coverage (asan / tsan / ubsan / memcheck) and
    cppcheck-clean sources.

